'''Glup!''' is a [[Chile]]an [[Rock music|rock]]-[[Pop music|pop]] band active in the period 1996-2003, with reunions in 2011, 2019 and from 2022 to the present. In 1999 the band performed at the [[Vi√±a del Mar International Song Festival]], after gaining mainstream popularity in Chile due to their adolescent lyrics and catchy melodies. [[Freebola]], released in 1999, was the group's commercial breakthrough and their [[List of signature songs|signature song]]. Primarily a [[Pop rock|pop-rock]] act, the band drew heavy inspiration from [[britpop]] scene.

